text.headline: crewai
text.text: CrewAI is a universal multi agent framework that allows for all agents to work together to automate tasks and solve problems.

text.headline: AutoGen
text.text: AutoGen provides multi-agent conversation framework as a high-level abstraction. With this framework, one can conveniently build LLM workflows.

text.headline: LangChain
text.text: LangChain provides tools and abstractions to improve the customization, accuracy, and relevancy of the information the models generate.
